{"tid":2562,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【色膽包天】全身塗黑僅穿內褲 印青年摸黑欲強姦女鄰居事敗逃去","createTime":"2016-11-25T23:06:17.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-26T08:58:05.000Z","uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a4404db868a4b14cfae97c308f068a3a33a0c045","tid":2562,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T23:06:17.000Z","msg":"<strong>【色膽包天】全身塗黑僅穿內褲 印青年摸黑欲強姦女鄰居事敗逃去</strong><br />\n<br />\n2016-11-26 04:11:00 HKT<br />\n<br />\n馬來西亞一名印度裔青年，涉嫌用汽車機油把全身塗黑，扮成所謂「油鬼仔」，深夜摸黑由屋頂潛入鄰居家中，企圖強姦女戶主，但事敗落荒而逃。<br />\n<br />\n案發時，男女戶主已入睡，但一對年幼子女還沒睡覺，他們聽到屋頂傳來走路聲，於是慌忙叫醒父母。男戶主到廚房查看，只遠遠見到對方僅穿一條內褲，全身塗黑。他喚醒鄰居協助搜捕，但仍被「油鬼仔」逃去。<br />\n<br />\n不過，男戶主在屋頂找到疑犯的衣物、手機和銀包，裏面有疑犯的身份證，證實屬居於附近一名21歲印度裔青年。<br />\n<br />\n警方相信疑犯是垂涎31歲女戶主的美色，欲深夜潛入施暴，唯未得手便行蹤敗露，正全力搜尋他歸案。"},{"pid":"4294e35f1883bd058e5857b85609c4b62e15c43a","tid":2562,"uid":63,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T23:10:46.000Z","msg":"睇得電視多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23bb95465dd27e6207c5f6e294348ce118f926b4","tid":2562,"uid":3179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T23:16:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4d8b110245f49643244f3ee4b4ad714b487f79c","tid":2562,"uid":4419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T23:20:14.000Z","msg":"無gif好失望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3a71887ca61d97b19bc0d6752fb220c490f6d69","tid":2562,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T23:26:31.000Z","msg":"成身油點姦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"468ba5defad9162c56cc9cafbd9854af497af4e6","tid":2562,"uid":8216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T23:33:57.000Z","msg":"本身都已經黑 仲要油黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14a5a148fe0fde9ea6530e45a3cc38ca90940239","tid":2562,"uid":1262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T23:36:57.000Z","msg":"Gif呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adb80d87b7658624cfd979835b7e66b0b99f8a7a","tid":2562,"uid":9282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T23:40:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPme8ejLJf9VJkwG7QjPmAwv8gpw7G6JUAkSntJn7rgVW?filename=C5u002.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC5u002.jpg&h=e929fff0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be0619c4a4d9aa9196c32dda28a7c1224b9f65ee","tid":2562,"uid":9017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T04:56:45.000Z","msg":"包公老強？？？"},{"pid":"618eccfd485f5d46b24e9256b5f9f98c3c4a5574","tid":2562,"uid":7004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T05:06:05.000Z","msg":"靚鄰居既圖呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a71acb657e8c88173586c1d741428addf228e51b","tid":2562,"uid":16792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T08:56:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmRSUwCot9uRxNgR8b87t3j1GF37LjM8EYJRAXiBQXMH7g?filename=6232QF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6232QF.jpg&h=6360d0f4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0cc737f9ad1dc7ecbf5d1cf511a26f2b47309442","tid":2562,"uid":6333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T08:57:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPme8ejLJf9VJkwG7QjPmAwv8gpw7G6JUAkSntJn7rgVW?filename=C5u002.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thu